38
00:02:17,357 --> 00:02:19,612
mitl-yorn a mentsh.

39
00:02:19,618 --> 00:02:21,755
er hot mikh gegibn a derze.

40
00:02:22,352 --> 00:02:24,180
hot er epes gezogt,

41
