fregt der bruder, "vos iz geshen?" zog ikh, "epes a daytsh redt tsu mir."

43
00:02:31,586 --> 00:02:34,685
zogt er, "er vet dir gornisht tun. lomir gibn a kuk."

44
00:02:34,685 --> 00:02:37,326
a klal, kukt er aroys, un ikh.

45
00:02:37,455 --> 00:02:38,675
fregt er

46
00:02:38,675 --> 00:02:42,388
dem bruder, "vos iz mit di MÄDCHEN? vos veynt zi?"

47
00:02:42,315 --> 00:02:44,391
 in DEUTSCH⟨UNK⟩n loshn?

48
00:02:43,864 --> 00:02:47,159
yo. ikh hob nisht gekent ⟨DEUTSCH⟩, nor kh'hob di verter,

49
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:49,070
