 un hot alts oysgefregt, vifl yor ikh bin alt, vifl dos. "SCHADE, SCHAD⟨E⟩."

69
00:04:07,014 --> 00:04:10,987
un drum iz undzer p-, poyezd avekgegan frier far zeyerer.

70
00:04:11,078 --> 00:04:14,362
gedenk ikh vi haynt vi er hot undz gezogt.

71
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:20,980
z-, azoy ⟨ot o⟩ hot er mir gemakht. ikh volt im haynt oykh derkent, nor vos? s'iz geven shoyn a mentsh in mitldike yorn.

72
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:26,740
zogt er, "a gliklekhe rayze tsu HAUSE!" ikh hob daytsh nokh nisht farshtanen, nit gevust,

73
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:29,021
nor dos hob ikh gedenkt ale yorn:

74
00:04:29,021 --> 00:04:31,695
a mentsh, az er tut i guts i shlekhts.

75
00:04:31,695 --> 00:04:33,059
guts geton.

76
00:04:33,100 --> 00:04:35,496
nisht ale zenen geven azoy.

77
00:04:35,496 --> 00:04:37,283
nu, dos iz geven fun oyvn,

78
00:04:37,283 --> 00:04:39,635
az me darf oyshargenen di yidn un shoyn.

79
00:04:39,635 --> 00:04:42,324
ze'mir gekumen tsu forn in dem Tultshin.

80
00:04:43,883 --> 00:04:44,909
dortn,

81
00:04:44,909 --> 00:04:46,813
a glik vos s'iz geven zumer,

82
00:04:47,005 --> 00:04:49,530
nor shreklekh. in barakn

83
00:04:50,008 --> 00:04:52,207
z⟨e'm-⟩ hot men undz arayngetribn,

84
00:04:52,207 --> 00:04:53,642
un in di barakn

85
00:04:53,642 --> 00:04:57,714
iz azoy ⟨ot o⟩, eyner ibern andern iz geven azoy, polkes.

86
00:04:58,007 --> 00:05:00,532
oyfzetsn hostu dikh nisht gekent.

87
00:05:00,707 --> 00:05:02,882
host dikh nisht gekent aniderzetsn.

88
00:05:02,882 --> 00:05:05,561
az du host gevolt, host nor azoy zikh gedarft araynrukn.

89
00:05:06,883 --> 00:05:11,720
un m'hot ongetribn mentshn dort fil. iker, mir ho'mir ongehoybn geyn oyf der arbet.

90
00:05:12,672 --> 00:05:15,271
nu, mikh hot men moyre gehat ibertsu-

91
00:05:17,262 --> 00:05:18,977
ibertsulozn oyf a minut,

92
00:05:19,438 --> 00:05:25,248
vayl ikh bin shoyn geven azoy, a meydl a untergevaksen⟨e un ale⟩. yeder fleg mikh fregn, fleg ikh zogn

