az ikh bin a kind. "ikh bin nokh a kind." un me fleg lakhn az m'hot mikh gezen.

94
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:33,186
yeder fleg kukn oyf mir; ikh bin geven azoy a,

95
00:05:33,208 --> 00:05:37,904
a meydl a sheyns. kh'hob gehat sheyne hor shvartse un ales. fleg yeder

96
00:05:37,904 --> 00:05:42,748
zikh opshteln. iz, di shvester mayne fleg mikh nit oplozn oyf a minut,

97
00:05:42,748 --> 00:05:45,555
vayl s'iz geven d⟨ort⟩ groyse umglikes. flegn

98
00:05:45,662 --> 00:05:47,799
araynkumen daytshn,

99
00:05:48,328 --> 00:05:51,614
 un Rumener. m'hot oysgekloybn di shenste meydlekh.

100
00:05:51,614 --> 00:05:55,303
m'hot gemakht fun zey khoyzek. me fleg zey aveknemen oyf gantse nekht

101
00:05:55,303 --> 00:05:58,374
un teg, un drum flegn zey kumen. s'iz geven

102
00:05:58,374 --> 00:05:59,454
shreklekh.

103
00:05:59,454 --> 00:06:01,850
fleg ikh geyn mit zey oyf der arbet.

104
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:04,877
dortn fleg men shteyn in vaser azoy ⟨ot o⟩,

105
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:07,239
un gegrobn dem torf.

106
00:06:07,853 --> 00:06:10,398
der torf iz geven blote shtiker.

107
00:06:10,398 --> 00:06:11,841
hot men gegrobn,

108
00:06:11,841 --> 00:06:16,067
un drum fleg men aroysnemen, un me fleg oyf di tatshkes

109
00:06:16,067 --> 00:06:19,844
tsunoyfleygn tsigelekh, zey zoln zikh oystrikenen oyf der zun.

110
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,236
fleg ikh geyn mit zey.

111
00:06:22,236 --> 00:06:26,330
zey hobn, m'hot getrogn, fleg ikh zitsn ⟨un⟩ tsunoyfleygn di tsigl.

112
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:30,150
oykhet di hentelekh kleyne, nas⟨e i⟩n blote,

113
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:31,725
