115
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:40,452
fleg men kokhn mamelige,

116
00:06:40,452 --> 00:06:42,789
azoy ⟨ot o⟩ oysgisn oyf a,

117
00:06:42,789 --> 00:06:46,031
 nu, oyf a,...

118
00:06:46,632 --> 00:06:47,824
oyf a plats?

119
00:06:47,307 --> 00:06:49,292
 oyf a lokshn-bret azoy.

120
00:06:47,948 --> 00:06:50,086
oyf a lokshn-bret. UNK.

121
00:06:49,973 --> 00:06:52,729
un di mamelige iz geven gekokht shiter,

122
00:06:52,729 --> 00:06:57,259
az ⟨se⟩ zol, az s'hot zikh oysgekilt, hot men gekent opnemen kvadratne shtiklekh.

123
00:06:57,259 --> 00:07:01,495
fleg men gibn kvadratne shtikl mamelige; dos iz geven ibern gantsn tog.

124
00:07:01,495 --> 00:07:05,121
un me fleg gibn, eynike mol, ferdn-fleysh,

125
00:07:05,245 --> 00:07:07,022
a shtikl ferdn-fleysh.

126
00:07:07,022 --> 00:07:10,779
nu, ven me zogt nit az s'iz ferdn-fleysh, efsher volt es yeder geke-

127
00:07:10,779 --> 00:07:15,086
eynike flegn esn. nu, ikh ken... ober avade iz nisht ⟨GDE⟩...

128
00:07:13,243 --> 00:07:14,023
ver,

129
00:07:14,023 --> 00:07:16,595
ver hot aykh dos esn derlangt?

130
00:07:17,108 --> 00:07:21,070
nu, dortn, vu m'hot gegrobn, se fleg zayn eyner

131
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,842
vos er hot geredt daytsh

132
00:07:22,842 --> 00:07:27,212
un fleg shrayen dortn ⟨u⟩n, UNK dortn mit alemen.

133
00:07:27,212 --> 00:07:28,610
iz, ⟨⟩,

134
