 azoy ken men... zey hobn gedarft koyln, zey hobn gedarft ales.

135
00:07:32,527 --> 00:07:35,487
azoy zhe vestu arbetn az me git nisht esn?

136
00:07:35,487 --> 00:07:37,503
iz dos flegn zey gibn eyn mol in tog.

137
00:07:37,503 --> 00:07:40,763
fleg men loyfn shteyn, ⟨iz⟩ in der sho hot men gemuzt uspeyen,

138
00:07:40,763 --> 00:07:42,476
ven s'iz geven,

139
00:07:42,476 --> 00:07:47,025
onbaysn tsayt. un az nisht, hostu dos, hos- s'hot dir nisht gestayet, "ay,

140
00:07:47,025 --> 00:07:48,111
gey vayter."

141
00:07:48,111 --> 00:07:50,632
nor mir fleg'mir dort arumert,

142
00:07:51,516 --> 00:07:55,478
 vu undz ze'mir gevoynt in di barakes, flegn mir geyn durkhn dorf

143
00:07:55,478 --> 00:07:58,530
atin oyf arbet. in der fri fleg men undz traybn,

144
00:07:58,671 --> 00:08:01,906
un krik oyf der nakht flegn mir geyn durkhn dorf.

145
00:08:02,012 --> 00:08:05,299
do ho'mir shoyn, a bisl bist durkhgegan,

146
00:08:05,299 --> 00:08:07,780
nor m'hot gelebt derfun vos m'hot gebetn.

147
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:12,683
fleg men zogn, "efsher host a LISHNIY shtikl broyt, gib. efsher hostu dos, gib."

148
00:08:12,683 --> 00:08:15,376
fleg ikh dort esn nor GOROKHn-broyt.

149
00:08:15,376 --> 00:08:18,408
GOROKHn-broyt, az kh'hob geesn, hob ikh shoyn nisht gevolt esn.

150
00:08:18,482 --> 00:08:23,137
zey hobn nisht gegesn. mir fleg men tomed zen, a shtikl GOROKHn-broyt, ikh zol esn.

151
00:08:23,137 --> 00:08:25,499
itster, az ikh ze GOROKH, ale yorn,

152
00:08:25,499 --> 00:08:29,401
kuk ikh oyf ⟨i⟩m nisht. azoy hob ikh zikh ongeesn mitn GOROKHn-broyt.

153
00:08:30,328 --> 00:08:34,147
azoy ze'mir opgeven dortn in dem, Tultshin

154
00:08:34,147 --> 00:08:35,418
biz in osyen.

155
00:08:36,488 --> 00:08:37,511
osyen.

156
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:39,286
s'iz kalt gevorn.

157
00:08:39,286 --> 00:08:42,118
s'iz farfroyrn gevorn. yeder hot gekhapt gute

158
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:46,758
shlafkeytn: der mit di fis hot shoyn nisht gekent geyn funem shteyn in vaser,

159
00:08:46,765 --> 00:08:48,683
un do funem esn.

160
00:08:49,684 --> 00:08:52,800
s'iz geven yents ruml in dem Tultshin oykhet.

161
00:08:53,397 --> 00:08:56,664
m'hot gemakht khoyzek fun yedn eynem:

162
00:08:56,704 --> 00:09:02,869
yidn, ven ze'mir gegan oyf di vegn, yidn mit di berder, fleg men nemen mit, tsigarn un zey

163
00:09:02,869 --> 00:09:04,326
unterreykhern.

164
00:09:04,602 --> 00:09:06,047
erlekhe yidn.

165
00:09:06,188 --> 00:09:10,086
ze'mir opgeven in dem Tultshin, iz geven same yunvar- yungvarg.

166
00:09:10,086 --> 00:09:10,923
yungvarg.

167
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:14,204
m'hot tsunoyfgenemen un m'hot undz krikgeshikt

168
00:09:15,132 --> 00:09:16,495
keyn Popovets.

169
00:09:16,495 --> 00:09:20,070
nu, ze'mir gekumen krik keyn Popovets. hot undz di

170
00:09:20,070 --> 00:09:22,367
baleboste krik arayngenemen.

171
00:09:22,367 --> 00:09:26,198
nu, un azoy ze'mir geven. mir fleg'mir geyn in di derfer,

172
00:09:26,198 --> 00:09:29,826
 do betn, do arbetn,

173
00:09:29,826 --> 00:09:33,556
un mir ho'mir zikh ernert. un do fleg men geyn grobn,

174
00:09:33,556 --> 00:09:37,590
un me fleg geyn ales, abi me zol iberlebn dos shtikl tsayt.

175
00:09:38,132 --> 00:09:43,495
un s'iz geven biter un fintster shoyn. naket bin ikh gegan, on a por zokn,

176
00:09:43,495 --> 00:09:47,653
un on shukhvarg, un on gornisht. un azoy ho'mir gelebt.

177
00:09:47,987 --> 00:09:50,816
un dernokh dem, az m'hot shoyn ongehoybn,

178
00:09:51,531 --> 00:09:53,870
di daytshn, tsu antloyfn,

179
00:09:53,893 --> 00:09:58,781
ho'mir ersht dentsmol moyre gehat. az zey flegn zikh dervisn, ergets iz do yidn, fleg ⟨me⟩n hargenen.

180
