un, un s'iz geven shreklekh. mir fleg'mir zikh ersht dentsmol shtark bahaltn.

181
00:10:05,368 --> 00:10:09,327
nor mir ho'mir gehert az, se geyt ales shoyn beser,

182
00:10:09,385 --> 00:10:11,862
un zey geyen tsurik. iz,

183
00:10:11,862 --> 00:10:14,458
⟨darf men⟩ zen, me zol blaybn lebn.

184
00:10:14,481 --> 00:10:16,803
in a tog zogt men az vos zey

185
00:10:16,803 --> 00:10:18,772
zenen shoyn avek, di rusishe,

186
00:10:18,772 --> 00:10:22,744
 di rusishe kumen arayn. un mir loyf'mir in shtot gibn a kuk:

187
00:10:24,623 --> 00:10:31,193
iz do shoyn epes a tsvey rusishe, un mir gey'mir krik. iz, di baleboste veynt un zogt az di daytshn

188
00:10:31,193 --> 00:10:33,150
loyfn iber dem dorf,

189
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:38,195
un me zukht yidn un me harget. "vuhin zent ir gegan? vos hot ir getun?

190
00:10:38,195 --> 00:10:43,714
 tsu vos zent ir gegan?" mir ho'mir azoy geveynt un zi gebetn, zi zol undz nit aroystraybn.

191
00:10:43,714 --> 00:10:46,527
un mir ho'mir zikh gebahaltn bay ir dortn vu,

192
00:10:46,527 --> 00:10:52,123
in a kamer ergets oyfn boydem, dort in a vinkl, in dem shtroy, tomer vet men kumen zukhn.

193
