di rusn?

196
00:10:58,841 --> 00:11:02,180
di rusishe. nu, azoy zenen arayngekumen,

197
00:11:03,672 --> 00:11:06,872
hot men nokh geshosn, s'iz ⟨g-⟩ nokh geven groyse tsores.

198
00:11:07,114 --> 00:11:10,382
undz ho'mir zikh oysgebahaltn dortn nokh

199
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:13,425
a sakh, un dernokh dem hot zi gezogt,

200
00:11:13,442 --> 00:11:18,408
ho'mir ge-, iz gevorn a prikaz, ven s'iz shoyn geven POLNOST'YU di

201
00:11:18,408 --> 00:11:22,129
rusishe, hobn zey gezogt az me zol nemen un me zol,

202
00:11:22,129 --> 00:11:24,425
 m'hot farnemen in der ARMII

203
00:11:24,597 --> 00:11:26,173
mayne brider.

204
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:30,267
men hot zey farnumen, ⟨ah, ⟩ far zelners?

205
00:11:28,478 --> 00:11:30,581
rusisher ARMII.

206
00:11:30,267 --> 00:11:32,285
in, in di rusishe ⟨ARMII⟩.

207
00:11:30,925 --> 00:11:33,562
 yo. nor s'hot nisht gedoyert keyn sakh;

208
00:11:33,562 --> 00:11:35,967
zenen tsugegan biz,

209
00:11:35,967 --> 00:11:38,529
Kamenits-Podolsk, hot men zey umgekert.

210
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:41,941
m'hot opgezogt az di vos zenen in di lagers

211
00:11:41,941 --> 00:11:43,560
zol men nisht nemen,

212
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,614
derfar vos,

213
00:11:45,614 --> 00:11:48,275
zey zoln zikh forn aheym, un fun der heym vet men nemen.

214
00:11:48,930 --> 00:11:51,475
nu, zenen mir opgeven nokh dortn...

215
00:11:51,475 --> 00:11:54,590
vifl zol ikh zogn? biz s'iz varem gevorn.

216
00:11:55,073 --> 00:11:56,976
nu, di baleboste,

217
00:11:56,976 --> 00:12:00,807
nu, PU- loz di erd ir zayn gring.

218
00:12:00,807 --> 00:12:03,237
zi hot undz zeyer fil geholfn.

219
00:12:03,237 --> 00:12:08,582
hot zi gezogt, un hot azoy geveynt ven ikh bin avekgef- ze'mir gegan, avekgeforn,

220
00:12:08,582 --> 00:12:11,287
un hot gezogt az ikh zol blaybn ir kind.

221
00:12:11,287 --> 00:12:16,138
zi hot ge- geheysn az zi iz a raykhe dort: zi hot a gortn, a shtub,

222
00:12:16,138 --> 00:12:18,323
mit alemen. zogt zi, "blayb!

223
00:12:18,323 --> 00:12:22,702
blayb! ikh'l dir shenken dem gortn, ikh'l dir khasene makhn, ikh'l dir ales."

224
00:12:22,702 --> 00:12:24,803
zog ikh, "ikh bin dokh a yidishke.

225
00:12:24,803 --> 00:12:25,732
un,

226
00:12:25,732 --> 00:12:30,352
azoy zhe...?" zogt zi, "vos du vest veln, vestu zayn, abi blayb." zog ikh, "neyn."

227
00:12:31,312 --> 00:12:32,827
 UNK...

228
00:12:31,455 --> 00:12:33,392
vi iz geven ir nomen?

229
00:12:33,345 --> 00:12:34,874
 YUZYA.

230
00:12:35,269 --> 00:12:37,187
nokh der milkhome,

231
00:12:38,586 --> 00:12:42,351
 s'iz avekgegan a tsvey yor, ze'mir gekumen tsu zikh,

232
00:12:42,508 --> 00:12:45,219
iz teykef ze'mir geforn atin tsu tsu.

233
00:12:46,086 --> 00:12:52,239
mir ho'mir dort opgeSNIMAET in dem kolkhoz vu mir ho'mir d- farloyrn dos shenste un dos beste,

234
00:12:52,347 --> 00:12:54,214
un vu m'hot zikh gemutshet,

235
00:12:54,321 --> 00:12:58,382
vu undz ze'mir geven, az undzere kinder zoln nokh a mol zen

236
00:12:58,459 --> 00:13:04,068
vos m'hot getun mit mentshn, un zoln nisht fargesn, un zeyere kindskinder dos zogn.

237
00:13:04,092 --> 00:13:07,680
ho'mir teykef opgeSNIMAET, un ikh hob dos bild.

238
00:13:07,838 --> 00:13:11,209
un mir fleg'mir, ze'mir geforn atin tsu tsu,

239
00:13:11,209 --> 00:13:14,753
derfar vos s'iz geven groyse masn-griber⟨s⟩ tsvey,

240
00:13:14,753 --> 00:13:17,284
un ⟨a s-⟩ shtark a sakh mentshn,

241
00:13:17,284 --> 00:13:22,124
un der kolkhoz, azoy ⟨zey zenen⟩ arayngekumen krik, di rusishe hobn ongehoybn grobn di erd.

242
00:13:22,215 --> 00:13:24,768
ho'mir moyre gehat, me zol dort nisht tsegrobn.

243
00:13:24,768 --> 00:13:28,742
ze'mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen, vifl s'iz geblibn, etlekhe kinder,

244
00:13:28,742 --> 00:13:33,290
genemen tsvey mashinen, ze'mir arayngeforn, arayngegan in kolkhoz.

245
00:13:33,290 --> 00:13:34,678
d⟨i⟩,

246
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:38,100
dortn hobn zey gevust az s'iz azoyns do geven,

247
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:41,069
az mentshn zenen oysgeshtorbn un ales,

248
00:13:41,069 --> 00:13:42,645
un mir ho'mir gebetn,

249
00:13:42,972 --> 00:13:45,396
me zol undz gibn helf, un mir zol'mir,

250
00:13:45,672 --> 00:13:49,195
far undzer gelt, mir zol'mir OGORO- arummakhn

251
00:13:49,195 --> 00:13:52,275
shtakhetn azoy, do vu s'iz di tsvey masn-griber,

252
00:13:52,275 --> 00:13:54,182
un zey zoln nisht grobn mer.

253
00:13:54,182 --> 00:13:56,246
un mir ho'mir dort ongeshribn

254
00:13:57,602 --> 00:14:02,528
az, vifl mentshn s'iz do un vi azoy zey zenen geshtorbn,

255
00:14:02,528 --> 00:14:06,658
farmutshete mentshn un ales, un flegn mir ale yor atin forn

256
00:14:06,715 --> 00:14:08,333
un zen,

257
00:14:08,333 --> 00:14:12,075
 d- oyf di pletser flegn mir geyn,

258
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:15,057
ontsindn likht, haltn yidishkeyt.

259
00:14:15,057 --> 00:14:17,503
un di mentshn vos hobn undz gut getun

260
00:14:17,503 --> 00:14:19,680
flegn mir keyn mol nisht fargesn.

261
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:22,802
ze'mir geforn, flegn mir onnemen fule mashinen

262
00:14:22,802 --> 00:14:24,758
mit,

263
00:14:26,104 --> 00:14:29,228
mit geshenken zey gibn ⟨un⟩,

264
00:14:29,228 --> 00:14:35,196
 vayl zey hobn gemeynt dentsmol az undz ze'mir VOOBSCHE epes nisht keyn mentshn. vos iz dos far a mentshn, vos zey zitsn

265
00:14:35,196 --> 00:14:37,488
un me tut zey azoyns un zey shvaygn?

266
00:14:38,826 --> 00:14:45,217
flegn mir ale yor forn. geforn farn avekforn ater, oykh geven dort oyf der erd, oyf der...

267
00:14:47,434 --> 00:14:56,017
un shtark a shlekhtn shikzal hob ikh gehat, UNK, aza milkhome iberlebn un azoy zen mit di oygn vos ikh hob gezen.

268
00:14:56,175 --> 00:14:59,787
nu, itster, danken got, ⟨kh'- b-⟩

269
00:14:59,787 --> 00:15:02,811
bin krank ale yorn fun dem lager

270
00:15:03,752 --> 00:15:09,005
un funem BRYUSHNOY tif. kh'hob opgelebt ale yorn un leb oyf shtrenge dyetes, un nisht

271
00:15:09,005 --> 00:15:14,732
gegesn azoy ⟨vi⟩ mentshn un nisht, gornisht vi mentshn, nor azoy leb ikh.

272
00:15:16,054 --> 00:15:17,148
froy Lipis,

273
00:15:17,148 --> 00:15:19,997
kh'volt gevolt visn az, hot ir,

274
00:15:20,222 --> 00:15:26,960
hot men aykh gezogt, ir zolt trogn a, a mogn-doved, dos heyst, dem JUDEN-shtern vos di DEUTSCHn hobn...

275
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,400
ir hot dos GEHABT?

276
00:15:27,850 --> 00:15:30,662
ven undz ze'mir in Sukeran,

277
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:33,669
iz mayn,

278
00:15:33,669 --> 00:15:38,566
 fleg geyn mit dermit, mayn bruder. ikh fleg in ergets nit aroysgeyn, gezesn in shtub.

279
00:15:38,566 --> 00:15:41,637
un er, az er iz aroysgegan, hot men gemuzt geyn mit dermit.

280
00:15:41,637 --> 00:15:43,708
iz gegan mitn mogn-doved.

281
00:15:43,948 --> 00:15:51,994
a altn pidzhak hot er epes getrofn, nor azoy hot men ongetun, ⟨hot,⟩ azoy hot men nisht getort aroy- oy! vifl m'hot im geshlogn, geharget!

282
00:15:51,994 --> 00:15:59,929
az er fleg aroysgeyn zen epes oyf tsu esn, fleg er aheymkumen blo! tsu tsvantsik nagaykes. vos m'hot gevolt hot men...

283
00:16:00,149 --> 00:16:03,281
un azoy fleg er loyfn; anisht volt'mir geven oysgeshtorbn.

284
00:16:05,076 --> 00:16:06,335
ven ir z-...

285
00:16:05,228 --> 00:16:08,496
shtark geven a shreklekh shtikl tsayt.

286
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:13,907
un far vos nor oyf di yidn iz dos geven, veys ikh nisht.

287
00:16:14,037 --> 00:16:15,550
un itstert...

288
00:16:16,298 --> 00:16:22,700
fun, fun Popovets zent ir s- gegangen tsurik aheym keyn NOWOSELITZA.

289
00:16:21,782 --> 00:16:27,948
fun Popovets ze'mir geforn keyn Ko- Kopaygorod. dortn iz a stantsye geven,

290
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:24,105
vi hot zikh dos...

291
00:16:27,948 --> 00:16:29,364
in Popovets nisht.

292
00:16:29,364 --> 00:16:32,055
un mir ho'mir zikh oyfgezetst oyf a vagon:

293
00:16:32,055 --> 00:16:37,514
vi, voser s'iz geven, mit V- mit VOENN⟨e⟩, mit vos, ⟨zey⟩ zenen geforn oyfn front.

294
00:16:37,514 --> 00:16:40,333
mir ho'mir uspeyet arayn. ze'mir arayn,

295
00:16:40,333 --> 00:16:43,309
⟨un⟩ ze'mir geforn biz keyn, Lipkan.

296
00:16:44,108 --> 00:16:49,091
un fun dortn ze'mir, geven a bisl in Lipkan. drum ze'mir avekgeforn keyn Tshernovits.

297
00:16:49,091 --> 00:16:50,984
in Tshernovits iz,

298
00:16:50,984 --> 00:16:52,708
ikh bin gegan in shkole.

299
00:16:52,815 --> 00:16:54,159
kh'hob gelernt.

300
00:16:54,385 --> 00:16:58,575
un, di shvester flegn arbetn. i eyne, i di andere

301
00:16:58,575 --> 00:17:00,330
hot ongehoybn arbetn.

302
00:17:00,330 --> 00:17:03,882
un drum ze'mir ibergeforn, zi hot khasene gehat, keyn Novoselits.

303
00:17:03,882 --> 00:17:09,102
bin ikh mit der klenerer geforn keyn Novoselits un ikh hob dort oykh gikh khasene gehat.

304
00:17:09,102 --> 00:17:11,055
ikh hob shtark yung khasene gehat,

305
00:17:11,055 --> 00:17:13,456
nokh keyn nayntsn yor nisht alt geven.

306
00:17:13,456 --> 00:17:17,456
mayn man iz geven alt dray un tsvontsik, oykhet nisht shtark...

307
00:17:17,148 --> 00:17:20,314
er iz oykhet geven fun NOWOSELITZA?

308
00:17:19,047 --> 00:17:24,723
er iz fun Novoselits geven, un hot gehat shtark a bitern lager oykh.

309
00:17:24,723 --> 00:17:27,153
nisht eyn mol iz dem, dem foter,

310
00:17:27,153 --> 00:17:31,943
hot men ongegibn az er iz a komunist. Avrom, hot er geheysn, Lipis.

311
00:17:31,982 --> 00:17:37,173
iz, hot men im opgeshlogn di lungen. m'hot im azoy lang geshlogn un er iz geshtorbn.

312
00:17:38,344 --> 00:17:41,808
shtark, ⟨,⟩ shreklekh geven, un fun zeyer,

313
00:17:41,808 --> 00:17:46,677
zenen geven shtark a s- a groyse familye, un m'iz geblibn zeyer vintsik.

314
00:17:46,677 --> 00:17:49,560
er iz mit der muter aheymgekumen mit der shvester.

315
00:17:49,566 --> 00:17:51,799
nu, di shvester iz geven

316
00:17:51,799 --> 00:17:53,110
gut gut,

317
00:17:53,110 --> 00:17:57,592
un der lager hot zikh, vayzt oys, ongerufn: bay zibn un draysik yor iz zi geshtorbn.

318
00:17:59,353 --> 00:18:00,899
ven hot ir...

319
00:17:59,771 --> 00:18:03,060
un er hot ⟨in⟩... nayn un fertsik yor.

320
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:08,487
hot zeyer fil mitgem- er fleg zingen azoyne lider funem lager.

321
00:18:08,487 --> 00:18:12,133
dortn in lager fleg men tsunoyfshteln yidishe lider,

322
00:18:12,133 --> 00:18:14,704
shtark sheyne un ⟨TRAUR⟩ike.

323
00:18:15,013 --> 00:18:17,288
 un er hot gekent shtark sheyn zingen.

324
00:18:17,288 --> 00:18:21,878
ikh gedenk zey nisht. kh'hob oykhet gevust, un di kinder hobn eynike rusishe gevust.

325
00:18:21,878 --> 00:18:23,101
zey hobn fargesn.

326
00:18:23,101 --> 00:18:28,257
fl- ikh fleg zogn, "me darf nisht, dermonen zikh. me darf nisht. se kost mikh gezunt."

327
00:18:28,257 --> 00:18:29,842
fleg im nisht lozn.

328
00:18:29,842 --> 00:18:32,416
nor er hot gekent zeyer fil lider.

329
00:18:32,416 --> 00:18:35,024
dortn fleg men zingen di lider,

330
00:18:35,024 --> 00:18:38,295
azoy m'hot, geharget un azoy di, di

331
00:18:38,368 --> 00:18:43,115
SHUTSMANY mit di NEMTSn zenen arayn in lager, un vos m'hot geton.

332
00:18:43,115 --> 00:18:48,218
er hot gekent zeyer fil, nor ⟨er iz⟩, er iz geven in der zayt fun Bershad.

333
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:54,401
shtark shver⟨n⟩ hobn zey gehat. ales oysgeshtorbn, a groyse mishpokhe geven.

334
00:18:55,108 --> 00:18:59,574
ve- ven hot ir ⟨khase- genah-⟩ khasene gehat? in velkhn yor?

335
00:18:58,134 --> 00:19:00,114
,

336
00:19:00,964 --> 00:19:02,412
 velkhn yor?

337
00:19:02,412 --> 00:19:06,094
UNK az ikh bin geven alt... ze, vos ikh veys shoyn nisht keyn...

338
00:19:04,710 --> 00:19:08,096
zent geven alt nayntsn yor, hot ir gezogt frieret?

339
00:19:06,690 --> 00:19:11,707
nayntsn, DA. UNK tsvey un draysik un, nayntsn...

340
00:19:12,439 --> 00:19:13,744
yo, s'iz

341
00:19:13,617 --> 00:19:14,947
..

342
00:19:13,744 --> 00:19:14,762
in...

343
00:19:15,342 --> 00:19:21,866
UNK men darf itst nikh- rekh- nisht rekhenen; me veys shoyn vi, ven ir hot gehat nayntsn yor, veys men vos...

344
00:19:20,456 --> 00:19:22,738
nayntsn yor bin ikh alt geven.

345
00:19:22,738 --> 00:19:25,376
nu, dos hob ikh khotsh gehat glik:

346
00:19:25,399 --> 00:19:28,838
a man zeyer a voyl⟨er⟩, un er hot mikh lib gehat.

347
00:19:28,838 --> 00:19:31,682
un s'iz bay undz geven aza familye,

348
00:19:31,682 --> 00:19:36,519
vos undz ⟨ho⟩'mir gevoynt in a kleyn shtetl, vos yeder fleg undz mekane zayn.

349
00:19:36,216 --> 00:19:40,901
dos iz NOWOSELITZA vayter geven? di shtot vos ir zent geboyrn ⟨gevorn⟩?

350
00:19:38,136 --> 00:19:39,250
yo.

351
00:19:39,250 --> 00:19:43,444
un di kinder mayne oysgelernt. zey hobn zeyer gut gelernt,

352
00:19:43,444 --> 00:19:46,571
un drum zenen zey geforn keyn Moskve shtudirn,

353
00:19:46,628 --> 00:19:47,975
un m'hot beyde...

354
00:19:47,975 --> 00:19:50,404
di tokhter iz a dokter,

355
00:19:50,404 --> 00:19:52,771
a ⟨ts-⟩ a tseyn-ARZT,

356
00:19:52,771 --> 00:19:57,382
un der zun hot gearbet in institut. er iz a ELEKTRONSHCHIK,

357
00:19:57,382 --> 00:20:00,723
a PROGRAMMIST. itster arbet er oykh shoyn do

358
00:20:00,723 --> 00:20:03,424
PROGRAMMIST, un fardint zeyer gut.

359
00:20:03,424 --> 00:20:05,921
 shtark voyle kinder, un

360
00:20:05,921 --> 00:20:09,541
ales iz geven gut, nor dos lebn iz bay mir geven a bisl kurts,

361
00:20:09,541 --> 00:20:11,971
un dos vos ale yorn bin ikh krank.

362
00:20:11,971 --> 00:20:15,933
nor az kh'hob ibergelebt azoyns, iz oykhet danken got.

363
00:20:16,918 --> 00:20:19,629
ir hot oykhet geARBEIT,...?

364
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:21,075
ale yorn hob ikh gearbet.

365
00:20:21,075 --> 00:20:24,467
nisht gezesn. fertsik yor hob ikh opgearbet,

366
00:20:24,467 --> 00:20:26,593
un gekhovet tsvey kinder oykh.

367
00:20:26,593 --> 00:20:29,538
gearbet a bukhhaltershe ale yorn.

368
00:20:29,538 --> 00:20:32,488
oyf eyn plats, eyn un draysik yor.

369
00:20:33,777 --> 00:20:35,593
hob ikh opgearbet.

370
00:20:36,207 --> 00:20:40,464
un drum hobn di kinder gezogt, me darf forn ater. forn, forn.

371
00:20:40,510 --> 00:20:43,645
mir iz shoyn alts eyns, abi zey zol zayn gut.

372
00:20:43,645 --> 00:20:47,088
un kh'hob moyre gehat shtark far di MESTNe mentshn,

373
00:20:47,088 --> 00:20:52,501
zey zoln nisht tun nokh a mol ot dos vos zey hobn getun a mol mit undz. di MESTNe dortn...

374
00:20:52,508 --> 00:20:55,370
ven undz ze'mir geven zayn in lager

375
00:20:55,370 --> 00:20:57,787
do in Novoselits un do arum,

376
00:20:57,787 --> 00:20:59,826
volt keyn eyner nisht geven geblibn lebn.

377
00:21:00,405 --> 00:21:03,785
nor dortn iz gebidevete mentshn geven,

378
00:21:03,785 --> 00:21:05,327
un zey flegn helfn.

379
00:21:05,670 --> 00:21:09,338
der hot gegibn a tepl milekh, der hot gegibn a shtikl broyt,

380
00:21:09,338 --> 00:21:14,219
vifl zey hobn gekent. zey hobn dokh nisht gekent undz hodeven; s'iz geven in tsayt fun der milkhome ⟨un s'iz⟩ geven shver.

381
00:21:14,631 --> 00:21:15,604
nu...

382
00:21:17,483 --> 00:21:21,830
vos k- vos klert ir, froy Lipis, vos hot es gemakht

383
00:21:21,921 --> 00:21:22,905
oyf aykh,

384
00:21:22,905 --> 00:21:27,511
az ir hot alts dos ibergelebt un ir zent a kind geven,

385
00:21:27,511 --> 00:21:32,394
ven ir hot gezen un derlebt al di zakhn, vos ir hot geredt UNK?

386
00:21:31,523 --> 00:21:33,187
itster vil ikh

387
00:21:33,413 --> 00:21:40,022
az, kinder, mayne kinder veln zeyer gut gedenken, vayl zey hobn zeyer fil gehert derfun.

388
00:21:40,095 --> 00:21:43,511
zey hobn gehert; der foter fleg tomed dertseyln,

389
00:21:43,511 --> 00:21:45,112
ikh, di bobe.

390
00:21:45,112 --> 00:21:50,242
